BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .145793 Tw (AI does not determine what is justified. It operates within the constraints defined by human authority. Without) Tj T* 0 Tw .987784 Tw (a human origin, there is no valid basis for action \227 not a weakened basis, not a provisional basis, but no) Tj T* 0 Tw .658427 Tw (basis at all. Legitimacy cannot be generated by the system itself. It must be received from a human source) Tj T* 0 Tw (and maintained throughout the life of every action taken in that authority's name.) Tj T* ET
