BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 1.184477 Tw (Each condition represents a necessary component of valid authority. The absence of any single condition) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.567805 Tw (invalidates the whole. Authority is not a spectrum \227 it does not exist partially or approximately. It either) Tj T* 0 Tw .144184 Tw (satisfies all four conditions or it does not exist. This is not a demanding standard imposed for its own sake \227) Tj T* 0 Tw (it reflects the structural reality of what legitimate authority actually requires.) Tj T* ET
