BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 2.263807 Tw (Voluntariness means the authorisation is freely given, without coercion, undue influence, or adversarial) Tj T* 0 Tw .580549 Tw (interference of any kind. An authorisation obtained through pressure, manipulation, or deception is not valid) Tj T* 0 Tw .706886 Tw (authority \227 it is the appearance of authority extracted under conditions that invalidate it. Systems must not) Tj T* 0 Tw (proceed on the basis of authorisations that were not freely given.) Tj T* ET
