BT 1 0 0 1 0 70.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .205977 Tw (Acting under uncertainty shifts risk from controlled to uncontrolled. A system that proceeds under uncertainty) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.462309 Tw (is not taking a cautious action and hoping for the best \227 it is taking an action whose authority status is) Tj T* 0 Tw .72164 Tw (unknown, and producing consequences whose legitimacy cannot be established. The system generates an) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.861136 Tw (outcome. The outcome affects people. And if the outcome is later found to have occurred without valid) Tj T* 0 Tw (authority, there is no remedy that fully addresses the harm already done.) Tj T* ET
